1. *Ričard* je bio veliki kralj Engleske. (Richard was a great king of England.)
2. Knjiga koju sam pročitao napisana je od strane *Ričarda* Džefersona. (The book I read was written by Richard Jefferson.)
3. Ulica *Ričarda* Lavljeg Srca je jedna od najpoznatijih ulica u Parizu. (The Richard the Lionheart Street is one of the most famous streets in Paris.)
4. Na fakultetu sam slušao predavanja profesora *Ričarda*. (I attended lectures by professor Richard at the university.)
5. *Ričardov* automobil je crvene boje. (Richard's car is red.)
6. *Ričardu* sam rekao da dođe u posjetu idućeg vikenda. (I told Richard to come visit next weekend.)
7. Danas sam se sreo s *Ričardom* na kafi. (I met with Richard for coffee today.)
8. Žena koju je *Ričard* upoznao sinoć je bila vrlo zanimljiva. (The woman Richard met last night was very interesting.)